name: gsdf/EasyNegative
description: The "gsdf/EasyNegative" dataset contains Negative Embeddings trained using the Counterfeit model. This dataset was created by gsdf and can be found in the "\stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings" folder. While it can be used with other models, its effectiveness may vary. The dataset includes the files "Counterfeit-V2.0.safetensors", "AbyssOrangeMix2_sfw.safetensors", and "anything-v4.0-pruned.safetensors". This dataset was modified on 2023-02-12 and was first created on 2023-02-01.
citeAs: @article{gsdf_easynegative,   title={gsdf/EasyNegative: A Dataset of Negative Embeddings Trained Using the Counterfeit Model},   author={gsdf},   year={2023},   month={02},   day={01},   url={https://huggingface.co/datasets/gsdf/EasyNegative}, }
creator: gsdf
keywords: Negative Embeddings, Counterfeit Model, Image Embeddings
